Cyber Claw:











Cyber Claw bounded out from the boulder, now feeling a little more free. She 
honestly didn't like to hide from battle, but she had no choice. The 
majority of her life lead to hiding, running and fighting for her very life. 
She charged a little ahead of Carnage.

"Let me approach them first," she said, then made a limp to her walk, 
putting more appearance to her damage. She had to pull this off.

She walked closer to the Ark, with her head down, walking to the main 
doorway of the ship. She had to know by now they could see her.
